nodes.title: Overnight Bangladesh ferry inferno kills dozens, injures scores more. Many passengers jumped off, swam ashore.

孟加拉国渡轮一夜之间发生火灾，造成数十人死亡，数十人受伤。许多乘客跳下船，游上岸。
